metadata.name: Crowning
metadata.description:
This digital mixed media artwork was created using a photograph that I took while out walking with my children a number of months ago. 

After taking the photo, I spent days editing the photo, painting digitally, and otherwise creating this image. 

While removing parts of the background that I did not want in the image, I purposely left digital lines and pixelation as an integral part of the artwork to show the digital nature of the piece and the process of the painting. 

Ashira Siegel Fox
2022
